        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"I am fatigued.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "Believe me, it is not fatigue that saddens you to night.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"What annoyance?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"That of this evening.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"Yes, you are right; but I do not think any danger is to be apprehended from Buckingham.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"No; still he is intrusive.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"What I said to him, count,\" replied Raoul, \"I will repeat to you. Listen to me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"Do you wish it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"I leave you, then,\" said Raoul, as he withdrew.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_75918_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/75918/6930_75918_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "The count advanced a step towards his friend, and pressed him warmly in his arms.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "They were certainly no nearer the solution of their problem.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "These two cherubic infants had both big brown eyes, fat red cheeks, and adorable, fluffy golden curls.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"The poor little things!\" cried Cynthia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"I've got it!\" she announced.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"You must be right,\" admitted Cynthia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"I thought we were 'stumped' again when I first saw that picture, but it's been of some use, after all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000006_000003",
