        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "But let's go and finish our studying now, and get that out of the way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "First they took turns sweeping, as best they could, with a very ancient and frowsy broom, the thick, moth eaten carpet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "But they'll have to do.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "I wonder, though, if people could see the light from the street, through any chinks in the boarding?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"Of course not,\" said Joyce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"Perhaps that's so,\" admitted Joyce, thoughtfully.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "There isn't a doubt but what that baby was she.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "\"I'm just dog tired!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6930_76324_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6930/76324/6930_76324_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6930",
        "content": "I just touched something soft!\" On the instant, Joyce was at her side with the candle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
